import axios from'axios';const API_KEY='YOUR_TRUSTPILOT_API_KEY';// Replace with your Trustpilot API key
const BASE_URL='https://api.trustpilot.com/v1';export const getTrustpilotReviews=async businessUnitId=>{try{const response=await axios.get("".concat(BASE_URL,"/business-units/").concat(businessUnitId,"/reviews"),{headers:{'Authorization':"Bearer ".concat(API_KEY)}});return response.data;}catch(error){console.error('Error fetching Trustpilot reviews:',error);return null;}};
